Exec
Reboot
Podcast
Rebooting
the
Leadership
Mindset
Bringing
the
C-suite
from
Financial
Institutions
together
to
rethink
financial
leadership
The
financial
world
is
changing
quickly,
and
it’s
difficult
to
keep
up.
Executives
of
modern
financial
institutions
face
a
myriad
of
challenges,
and
it
can
be
difficult
to
find
the
next
path
forward.
Finovate’s
Exec
Reboot
program
is
an
invite-only
initiative
bringing
C-suite
executives
together
to
re-examine
their
leadership
strategy
and
share
best
practices
in
a
peer
to
peer
setting.
What
to
Expect:
Our
CxO
guests
will
have
an
opportunity
to
join
closed-door
strategy
sessions,
thought-provoking
chats
with
industry
leaders
and
keynotes.
Plus
off-the-record
boardroom
brainstorm
sessions
and
private
networking
that
will
refuel
and
re-energise.
Highlights
include:
Staying
ahead
of
the
digital
transformation
curve
The
transformation
of
customer
relationships
–
when
digital
becomes
human
How
to
prepare
your
business
for
the
next
2-10
years
Get
Involved
The
Exec
Reboot
program
is
invitation
only
for
C-Suite
of
Banks
and
Financial
Institutions.
Participation
is
curated
for
an
optimal
balance
of
perspectives
and
experiences.
To
request
an
invitation,
click
on
the
corresponding
show
button
below:
